verses.text: \w A|strong="H7121"\w* psalm \w for|strong="H7121"\w* \w David|strong="H1732"\w*, \w at|strong="H0413"\w* \w the|strong="H0413"\w* finishing \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H0413"\w* tabernacle. \w Bring|strong="H3381"\w* \w to|strong="H0413"\w* \w the|strong="H0413"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w*, \w O|strong="H3068"\w* ye children \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w God|strong="H3068"\w*: \w bring|strong="H3381"\w* \w to|strong="H0413"\w* \w the|strong="H0413"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H0413"\w* offspring \w of|strong="H3068"\w* rams.

\w Bring|strong="H5375"\w* \w to|strong="H0413"\w* \w the|strong="H0413"\w* Lord glory \w and|strong="H3027"\w* honour: \w bring|strong="H5375"\w* \w to|strong="H0413"\w* \w the|strong="H0413"\w* Lord glory \w to|strong="H0413"\w* \w his|strong="H5375"\w* name: adore ye \w the|strong="H0413"\w* Lord \w in|strong="H0413"\w* \w his|strong="H5375"\w* \w holy|strong="H6944"\w* court.

\w The|strong="H5973"\w* voice \w of|strong="H6466"\w* \w the|strong="H5973"\w* Lord \w is|strong="H7563"\w* upon \w the|strong="H5973"\w* waters; \w the|strong="H5973"\w* God \w of|strong="H6466"\w* majesty hath thundered, \w The|strong="H5973"\w* Lord \w is|strong="H7563"\w* upon many waters.

\w The|strong="H5414"\w* voice \w of|strong="H3027"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* Lord \w is|strong="H3027"\w* \w in|strong="H7725"\w* \w power|strong="H3027"\w*; \w the|strong="H5414"\w* voice \w of|strong="H3027"\w* \w the|strong="H5414"\w* Lord \w in|strong="H7725"\w* magnificence.

\w The|strong="H3588"\w* voice \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w* breaketh \w the|strong="H3588"\w* cedars: \w yea|strong="H3588"\w*, \w the|strong="H3588"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w* \w shall|strong="H3068"\w* \w break|strong="H2040"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* cedars \w of|strong="H3068"\w* Libanus.

\w And|strong="H3068"\w* \w shall|strong="H3068"\w* reduce \w them|strong="H1288"\w* \w to|strong="H3068"\w* pieces, \w as|strong="H3068"\w* \w a|strong="H3588"\w* calf \w of|strong="H3068"\w* Libanus, \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w as|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3588"\w* beloved son \w of|strong="H3068"\w* unicorns.
\w The|strong="H3068"\w* voice \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w* divideth \w the|strong="H3068"\w* flame \w of|strong="H3068"\w* fire:

\w The|strong="H3068"\w* voice \w of|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w* shaketh \w the|strong="H3068"\w* desert: \w and|strong="H3068"\w* \w the|strong="H3068"\w* \w Lord|strong="H3068"\w* \w shall|strong="H3068"\w* shake \w the|strong="H3068"\w* desert \w of|strong="H3068"\w* Cades.

\w The|strong="H0853"\w* voice \w of|strong="H5159"\w* \w the|strong="H0853"\w* Lord prepareth \w the|strong="H0853"\w* stags: \w and|strong="H5769"\w* \w he|strong="H5704"\w* \w will|strong="H5704"\w* discover \w the|strong="H0853"\w* thick woods: \w and|strong="H5769"\w* \w in|strong="H5159"\w* \w his|strong="H5375"\w* temple \w all|strong="H5704"\w* \w shall|strong="H5159"\w* speak \w his|strong="H5375"\w* glory.
The Lord maketh the flood to dwell: and the Lord shall sit king for ever.
The Lord will give strength to his people: the Lord will bless his people with peace.
